#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/pricing/pricing_and_faq.rst:0
msgid "**Do I receive an invoice to buy my credits?**"
msgstr "**¿Recibo una factura al comprar mis créditos?**"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/pricing/pricing_and_faq.rst:0
